                <p>Students are solely responsible for the content they submit. They will be held accountable for any inaccuracies or misleading information in their course submissions.</p>
                <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
                <p>Students must ensure that the course content and materials do not violate any copyrights or intellectual property rights. They must own the rights or have permission to use any content they submit.</p>
                <h2>4. Review and Approval</h2>
                <p>All courses submitted by students are subject to review and approval by our team. We reserve the right to verify the information before publishing the courses on our platform.</p>
                <h2>5. Compliance with Policies</h2>
                <p>Students must comply with all platform policies, including those related to acceptable content, privacy, and data protection. Violations of these policies may result in the removal of the course or other actions.</p>
                <h2>6. Disclaimers</h2>
                <p>We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or usefulness of the courses submitted by students. The platform is not liable for any inaccuracies or issues arising from the content submitted by students.</p>
                <h2>7. Consequences of Violation</h2>
                <p>Violating these terms and conditions may result in consequences such as the removal of courses, account suspension, or legal action, depending on the severity of the violation.</p>
                <h2>8. Modification of Terms</h2>
                <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms and conditions at any time. Students will be notified of any changes and must agree to the updated terms to continue submitting courses.</p>
                <h2>9. Contact Information</h2>
                <p>If students have any questions or concerns regarding the course submission process, they can contact us at [insert contact information].</p>
            </div>
            <a asp-action="addcourse" asp-controller="course" class="btn-dark mt-4">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
